{"id":4587,"date":"2018-10-30T15:30:26","date_gmt":"2018-10-30T19:30:26","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/staging.cegepsl.qc.ca\/nouvelle\/congres-de-lassociation-de-mathematiques-du-quebec-au-cegep-de-saint-laurent\/"},"modified":"2023-06-14T13:19:15","modified_gmt":"2023-06-14T17:19:15","slug":"congres-de-lassociation-de-mathematiques-du-quebec-au-cegep-de-saint-laurent","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/nouvelle\/congres-de-lassociation-de-mathematiques-du-quebec-au-cegep-de-saint-laurent\/","title":{"rendered":"Congr\u00e8s de l&rsquo;Association de math\u00e9matiques du Qu\u00e9bec au c\u00e9gep de Saint-Laurent"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>C\u2019est au c\u00e9gep de Saint-Laurent que s\u2019est tenu, du 12 au 14 octobre, le 62<sup>e<\/sup> Congr\u00e8s de l\u2019<a href=\"https:\/\/www.amq.math.ca\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Association Math\u00e9matique du Qu\u00e9bec (AMQ)<\/a>, auquel ont pris part pr\u00e8s de 200 enseignantes et enseignants de math\u00e9matique des niveaux coll\u00e9gial et primaire pour discuter de \u00ab dimensions \u00bb.<br \/>\nLes participantes et participants ont soulign\u00e9 la qualit\u00e9 de la r\u00e9ception des organisatrices et organisateurs du Coll\u00e8ge. La direction tient d\u2019ailleurs \u00e0 remercier tous membres du <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/departements\/mathematiques\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">D\u00e9partement de math\u00e9matiques<\/a> qui ont travaill\u00e9 toute l\u2019ann\u00e9e \u00e0 l\u2019organisation de cet \u00e9v\u00e9nement d\u2019envergure. Leur engagement aupr\u00e8s des congressistes s\u2019est av\u00e9r\u00e9 aussi solide que celui dont ils font preuve quotidiennement aupr\u00e8s des \u00e9tudiants et \u00e9tudiantes du Coll\u00e8ge.<br \/>\nEnfin, nous tenons \u00e0 f\u00e9liciter et \u00e0 remercier plus particuli\u00e8rement Dimitri Zuchowski, Yannick Delbecque, G\u00e9raldine Martin et Cl\u00e9ment Hyvrier pour cette r\u00e9ussite.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>C\u2019est au c\u00e9gep de Saint-Laurent que s\u2019est tenu, du 12 au 14 octobre, le 62e Congr\u00e8s de l\u2019Association Math\u00e9matique du Qu\u00e9bec (AMQ), auquel ont pris part pr\u00e8s de 200 enseignantes et enseignants de math\u00e9matique des niveaux coll\u00e9gial et primaire pour discuter de \u00ab dimensions \u00bb.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":5843,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[15],"sujet-actualite":[197],"etiquette-interne":[2305],"class_list":["post-4587","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-nouvelle","sujet-actualite-institutionnel","etiquette-interne-institutionnel"],"acf":[],"publishpress_future_action":{"enabled":false,"date":"2026-05-05 21:35:00","action":"change-status","newStatus":"draft","terms":[],"taxonomy":"category"},"publishpress_future_workflow_manual_trigger":{"enabledWorkflows":[]},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4587","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4587"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4587\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4902,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4587\/revisions\/4902"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/5843"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/